Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:06.44,Tea on Rice,Sign 0001,0014,0001,0025,,{\an8}{\fad(777,1144)}What is the Ideal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:03.52,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What is the Ideal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:06.26,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,There are any number of \Nanswers to that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:08.67,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,It is words,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.24,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,it is thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.70,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,It is the font of all meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.11,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,But if you were to ask me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:16.78,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,the answer to the question is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:22.87,ideal - darker,Sign 0018,0138,0001,0157,,{\an8}Ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:21.48,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,It is the word written \Non my notebook's cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:25.69,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,The Ideal...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:29.12,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Everything about me is \Nwritten in this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:29.84,ideal - darker,,0010,0001,0086,,{\an8}Ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:33.43,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,My schedule, my plans, my goals...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:37.30,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook contains the \Nentirety of my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:18.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I arrived a whole ten seconds early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:21.00,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kunikida Doppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.68,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I am an idealist walking the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:25.68,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,and a pragmatist in pursuit of ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:28.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:30.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san, please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:34.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on so early in the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:37.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,J-J-Just look at Dazai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:37.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:40.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun, it's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:42.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:44.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,At that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I only see your idiot face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.83,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.03,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:51.30,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,At Yomotsuhirasaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:52.45,Stray Dogs - Top,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as I'd imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:53.94,Stray Dogs - Top,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Blue smoke trailing along the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:54.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.56,Stray Dogs - Top,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,moonlight dashing against the windows,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:56.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I think this may explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.49,Stray Dogs - Top,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and pink elephants dancing \Nin the western sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:57.78,complete guide to suicice,Sign 0257,0266,0001,0161,,Complete Guide \Nto Suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:01.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I knew the {\i1}Complete Guide to Suicide{\i0}\N was a masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew I just needed to eat mushrooms \Ngrowing in the nearby hills
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,to have such an entertaining way out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:09.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So he ate poisonous mushrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:12.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he thought he was eating \Nlethal mushrooms, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:14.31,Stray Dogs - Top,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I've finally caught you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.00,Stray Dogs - Top,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,rainbow pillbug!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's eat you back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.83,Stray Dogs - Top,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:20.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing my customary paperwork \Nafter arriving at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:21.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Wait till I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:34.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You should come to the afterlife, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:35.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:38.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,There are rainbow pillbugs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You can drink all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:44.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You can eat all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:48.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You can look at all the sleeping \Nbeauties you could possibly—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:55.37,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Why are two such incompatible \Npeople a team?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:04:00.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san, the president \Nhas your case for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:03.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Quit dawdling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Walk faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:10.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We only have two minutes and fifteen \Nseconds until the appointed time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's a concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for me to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,This is part of your rookie training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:20.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,This case involves solving a series \Nof disappearances in Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:24.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, it's the one \Nwhere visitors to Yokohama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:27.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,keep disappearing one after another, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We have an anonymous tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:34.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,The victims have been abducted and \Nimprisoned in a certain location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,An anonymous tip...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:39.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,How suspicious and wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:41.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to check the place out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to investigate the \Nanonymous tip's source first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,How goes it, informant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:03.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, four-eyes. Are you a slave \Nto your notebook yet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:06.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can talk like \Nthat to a detective agency
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,when you're a cyber criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,If you're arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,your deceased father will be most aggrieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring my father into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that unusual for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:19.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Were you on a date with a pretty lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:21.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:24.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Dates should be with a chosen woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,followed by marriage six years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,That is what's written in this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:32.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You have someone you've decided to marry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I will in another four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Is he new?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:39.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nakajima Atsushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:43.40,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 0543,0001,0442,0048,,{\an8}Cyber Network Warrior \N Taguchi Rokuzou
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm called Taguchi Rokuzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an informant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,For the right price, I can \Ndig up dirt on anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:47.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:49.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Did you figure out who's \Nbehind the anonymous tip?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,The Azure Messenger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:52.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,There was data left on the server.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,And pics of the abduction victims, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:01.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,The mole's not a bad guy, though, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:04.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,He told you where they're holed up and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:10.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we don't go there, only to \Nfind he's one of the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,The Azure Messenger...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to keep looking into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:22.52,Stray Dogs Ep Title,Sign 0621,0104,0001,0048,,Episode 6 \N The Azure Messenger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:21.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy looking after my tropical fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:23.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:25.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I called a cab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:30.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go to the abandoned hospital \Nmentioned by the tipster now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:34.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun, why are you \Nlooking after the Rokuzou boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:40.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to give a hacker jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You could've just talked \Nto him over the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:44.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but you took the time to \Nmeet him face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,His father's deceased, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to be his dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:53.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We came here so that Atsushi \Ncould meet our informant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:57.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, let's leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:06.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,This driver's another one of our informants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,He was a stage actor in his former life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't make any money,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:11.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,so I switched careers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:13.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,That was the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:17.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,He knows more about Yokohama \Nthan anyone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:24.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,He also saw two of the eleven victims \Nright before they were abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:29.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to drive them \Nfrom the port to a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Is this case really about \Nabductions, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,There've been no requests for ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:36.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure these two \Nwere the ones you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,They're even wearing the same clothes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I have a hunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:47.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Look at these photos. \NThey're both wearing glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:49.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That means this is a serial \Nglasses abduction case!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:52.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's your time to shine, Kunikida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:55.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Some of the victims don't wear glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:56.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say it's a pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:01.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad. And here I thought it'd \Nfinally be your time to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:04.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that remark pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say my glasses are the \Nonly reason I'd ever be in the spotlight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:11.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:15.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,It's the abandoned hospital, as you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I think it might be haunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,By what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,It is creepy, to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:27.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It revs you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:31.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not have eaten \Nanother weird mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:34.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you scared, Kunikida-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of ghosts or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:39.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Then keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:43.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,In this sort of movie, those who are \Ncareless and get ahead of themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,are the ones who die first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Look at these footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:48.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,They're still fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Did it come from the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:56.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:16.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:22.75,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 0917,0001,0446,0049,,{\an8}University Lecturer \NSasaki Nobuko
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:18.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I am Sasaki Nobuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a lecturer at a university in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:25.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,So you're victim number twelve?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see who abducted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:32.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I blacked out at a station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,When I regained consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I was drowning in the tank, as you just saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:39.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai, what's your take on the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki-san's looking super sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:44.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:48.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,There should be others \Nwho were abducted here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:52.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I know I heard voices just as \NI began drowning in the tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:09:59.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:03.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:06.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Get us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Get back, Atsushi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:11.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Kunikida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:14.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:15.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:16.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, Dazai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:20.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,People shouldn't die like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:20.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:22.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:32.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,"Victims of Yokohama's serial abduction case were found,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.86,Tea on Rice,Sign 1033,0001,0326,0022,,{\an8}Series of Disappearances in \NYokohama Ends in Tragic Deaths
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:35.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,but perished when a civilian detective agency \Nconducted an independent raid."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Perished...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So this was the enemy's objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:44.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying they were \Ntrying to frame the Agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:51.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it wasn't my time to shine, \Ndespite what Dazai said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:52.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:56.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ms. Sasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:11:01.41,infirm,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,She should be in the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:03.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for \Nsaving me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't come when you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be alive right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:14.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:18.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, you even let me \Nstay at your residence last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:19.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:22.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,My place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.20,Stray Dogs - Default,NK,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:28.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... deeply indebted to Dazai-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:29.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:33.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that something detectives \Nare allowed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:37.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Sasaki-san didn't see who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,She apparently faints a \Nlot due to anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:45.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she fainted on\Nthe day she was abducted, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how she was abducted afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:50.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So she's your type?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:52.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I like all women.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:56.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But Sasaki-san seems like the type \Nwho'd commit suicide with me if I ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:58.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,which is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:00.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But what about you, Kunikida-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Is she your type?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:04.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,She is a victim in the case \Nand a witness. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:07.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's how you would roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:10.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Atsushi-kun, want to read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.21,ideal,Sign,0001,0418,0123,,Ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:12.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,His ideal woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:13.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,When'd you swipe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:17.21,ideal,,0338,0001,0044,,{\an8}Ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Read? You mean it's \Nwritten down in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun's notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:23.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,has a wide range of schedules, \Nplans, and ideals recorded in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:24.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,See, like here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:25.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.49,ideal,,0001,0454,0094,,Ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You have a problem with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:36.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can sympathize with your \Nvision of an ideal woman, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:40.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably not share \Nthat vision with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about the \Nabductions right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:46.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Have we picked up on anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:46.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,In this newspaper photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,you look pretty manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:54.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your way of indicating \Nthat you want me to punch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:56.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What's regrettable is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You should've picked \Nsexier eyeglass frames
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:01.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,if you were going to end up in the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,They're so plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:02.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:06.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Only a naturally flamboyant person \Nlike me could pull off wearing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Atsushi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,They only scream "con man" to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:15.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I know who's behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:32.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,You said on the phone that you'd figured \Nout who's behind the serial murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:35.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,You're on your way to arrest the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:37.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:39.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:40.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:42.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the abductions took place,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:43.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,and you are the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You dosed passengers with sleeping gas,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,and abduct them after they fell unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:52.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You wore a gas mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What were his reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I can think of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:58.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:13:59.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Cargo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He'd sell them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,There's a black market for \Norgans in the underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:10.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The margin isn't great because of the exchange rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're pulling it off alone,\N it's a decent payout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:19.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd used this taxi to abduct people,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:22.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,the city police would've found me already \Nwhen tracing the victims' last known locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:25.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,No, no one looked twice at this taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:32.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Because all the victims would vanish and \Nbecome untraceable the following day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:35.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,When your targets boarded the taxi \Nand you made them unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:38.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,you'd imprison them and take \Ntheir clothes and luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:43.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,That's why all the victims at the \Nhospital were in their underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You would then wear their clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,to disguise yourself as them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,then check into the hotels where \Nthey'd made reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You made sure you would show up on \Nsecurity cameras for that reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:55.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,The victims were all of approximately \Nthe same height and build
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:59.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,because you were choosing passengers \Nyou could impersonate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:02.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Many wore hats and glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:04.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,because that made passing \Nyourself off as them easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:09.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,If the security feeds show someone \Nlooking reasonably like the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,you can dupe the police easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:14.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,By the time the last known sighting \Nof the "victim" was recorded,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:18.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,the real victim had already been abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:21.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Sasaki's abduction was \Neven easier, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,After she collapsed at the train station,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:28.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,a good Samaritan paid for her cab ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's faster to hail a cab than call \Nan ambulance at a train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,That's all circumstantial evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What now, Kunikida-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:43.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Are you being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:45.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:46.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,A deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:49.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,If you agree to my conditions, \NI'll turn myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:52.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect me at the \NArmed Detective Agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:56.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be protected for 72 hours while \Nthe prosecution concludes their questioning
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,and arranges witness protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:15:59.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I was put up to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I was assured by a new-fangled \Norgan smuggling organization
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:08.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,that this was a great deal I'd \Nnever get caught for, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So there's a group behind all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:13.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:16.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I always meet them in the\N Harbor Central Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:19.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:21.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you need our protection?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,It appears one of the people I abducted
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,was with the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not good—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:35.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,The Port Mafia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:35.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:35.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:36.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:38.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:40.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:44.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,They must be jamming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose the driver,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,the truth may never come to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai, pursue the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Brat, get a hold of the \Npolice and request backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I'll distract them as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:53.48,Stray Dogs - Default,DN,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:54.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:57.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Ability: Doppo Poet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.91,No Longer Human,Sign 1657,0008,0001,0021,,{\an8}{\fad(652,1)}Doppo Poet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:01.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Flash Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:02.87,sign_31821_418_Wire_Gun,Sign,0001,0412,0138,,{\an8}{\fad(1,224)}Flash Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,Metal is fragile,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,and so is the human psyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:26.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,What about you all, Armed Detective Agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:29.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Akutagawa of the Port Mafia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:30.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't shoot straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:45.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,there's no need for me to devour\N the space around your bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:48.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,My hobbies don't include murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:50.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,Trifling words of a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Doppo Poet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:01.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Stun gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:04.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Come to heel, you aberrant dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:19.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the Armed Detective Agency \Nis not merely a group of entertainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,You're worthy of being Dazai-san's cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,Interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,Our paths will cross again in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0000,0000,0000,,We'll continue this another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I turned the driver over \Nto the military police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:48.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the building the organ \Ntraffickers used for their deals?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:54.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,They've already flown the coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,The wall's scorched black.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:19:00.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the Azure \NKing blew himself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:01.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:01.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:04.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, the one in the infamous \NAzure Flag terrorist incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:06.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0} Azure King?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:07.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:15.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,A terrorist who destroyed many \Nnational and corporate facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:15.21,Tea on Rice,Sign 1913,0001,0114,0035,,{\an8}Azure Flag Terrorist Incident
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:18.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,From the time I heard the \Nterm "Azure Messenger,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:22.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering if there \Nwere ties to the Azure King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:25.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that the Azure King \Nblew himself up in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,So this was the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:31.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,He committed suicide after the \Npolice cornered him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:32.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:35.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I'd determined that this was his hideout
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:37.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,and reported it to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:41.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who found \Nthe Azure King's hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:43.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,But on that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,the military, the public safety bureau, and \Nthe police were all working in tandem,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:48.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,so the chain of command was in utter chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:54.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Only five detectives arrived at the hideout \Nin a timely manner upon receiving the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,To add further insult to injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:20:01.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,the Azure King got wind \Nof the police's actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:04.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,so he holed himself up with a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:06.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,After a conflicting set of orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,a decision was made to raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:13.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,But ordinary policemen without special\N training or abilities didn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:20.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Cornered, the Azure King blew \Nhimself up and perished,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:22.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,along with the five detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now, Kunikida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:31.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,One of the detectives was that \NRokuzou boy's father, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:34.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,He was a good detective with \Na strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who reported the \Nhideout's location to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:40.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I may as well have set the bomb off myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:41.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,It's the terrorist's fault \Nfor blowing himself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:46.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:51.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yet Kunikida-kun can't stop trying \Nto look out for the Rokuzou boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,in his deceased father's stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:20:58.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:04.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Another job for the Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,The client...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.32,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 2106,0001,0086,0077,,{\an8}Regards, \NThe Azure Messenger
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,is the Azure Messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:09.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:11.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to see who \Nthis Azure Messenger is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:13.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,So? What's the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Disarming a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:19.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't disarm the \Nbomb by sunset tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,several hundred people will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb capable of that can't be easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:26.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,The equipment here is for building a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,With this setup,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:31.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,you could build a very advanced bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:32.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We won't let the bomb go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:39.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop it for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:11.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.01,0:23:14.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't find and disarm \Nthe bomb by sundown,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:16.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,there will be hundreds of casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.28,0:23:18.01,Stray Dogs - Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,If we cannot find the bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:20.24,Stray Dogs - Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,and lives are lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:22.52,Stray Dogs - Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,we no longer have the right to call \Nourselves a detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:24.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:28.39,Stray Dogs - Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,Think of this mission as a fight for \Nthe Agency's existence and pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:29.49,Stray Dogs - Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:33.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Man, where'd Dazai-san run \Noff to now, of all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:37.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Bungo Stray Dogs, Episode 7:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.21,0:23:38.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Love for the Disease Called Ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:38.93,Stray Dogs Next ep title,Sign 2338,0001,0001,0032,,{\an8}Episode 7 \N Love for the Disease Called Ideals
